# Security headers for the INTERNAL admin (Cloudflare Pages edge).
# Keep it out of search engines; real access control is Cloudflare Access + the
# backend (security.md §3). CSP omitted here — add a tuned policy before production.
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
